Package: FacileDataSet
Type: Package
Title: Provides an API for fluent and chainable interaction with genomics data,
    and a datasetore that implements this API to work with muthatand (warehouse for molecular clinical trial data to enable EDA
Version: 0.7.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Steve", "Lianoglou", , "slianoglou@gmail.com", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Vincent", "Rouilly", , "rouilly.vincent@gene.com", role = "ctb"),
    person("Genentech", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: An abstraction of an ExpressionSet-like object into a "tidy data"
  framework which allows effortless access into any subset of it without loading
  it in its entireity.
